OL,3,CSwansea maternity review 'a disaster'
OL,4,Cparents say
OL,6,FAn independent review of maternity and
OL,7,Fneonatal services at Swansea Bay
OL,8,FUniversity Health Board has been
OL,9,Flabelled 'a disaster' by angry parents.
OL,11,FThe health board announced in December
OL,12,Fa review was needed "in order to
OL,13,Fmaintain the public confidence in the
OL,14,Fcare being delivered."
OL,16,FIt followed an ITV Wales This Week
OL,17,Finvestigation that found critical
OL,18,Fissues within the maternity unit at
OL,19,FSingleton Hospital and a Healthcare
OL,20,FInspectorate Wales report which found
OL,21,Fthe unit to be "unsafe".
