OL,3,CSwansea maternity review 'a disaster'
OL,4,Cparents say
OL,6,FRobert Channon's son Gethin was born
OL,7,Fwith severe brain damage after
OL,8,Fcomplications with his birth at
OL,9,FSingleton Hospital in 2019. A review
OL,10,Fby the health board into his birth was
OL,11,Fheavily criticised by one of the UK's
OL,12,Ftop medical investigators Dr Bill
OL,13,FKirkup.
OL,15,FMr Channon says he's angry that no
OL,16,Fprogress has been made six months on
OL,17,Ffrom the announcement of a review into
OL,18,Fmaternity services in Swansea.
