OL,3,CSwansea maternity review 'a disaster'
OL,4,Cparents say
OL,6,F"We had some real hope that we were
OL,7,Fgoing to get some answers, not just
OL,8,Ffor us but for all the families
OL,9,Finvolved...but it's turned out to be a
OL,10,Fdisaster" he told ITV Wales.
OL,12,F"It's been a painful disaster for
OL,13,Ffamilies who wanted to participate in
OL,14,Fit as there's been no participation."
OL,16,FFollowing the departure of Ms Bowron
OL,17,Fthe health board have appointed
OL,18,Fmidwife Dr Denise Chaffer on an
OL,19,Finterim basis.
