OL,3,CSwansea maternity review 'a disaster'
OL,4,Cparents say
OL,6,F"We know that the situation in the
OL,7,FSingleton Maternity Unit is still
OL,8,Fcritical today. We know there is a HIW
OL,9,Finspection report coming up that found
OL,10,Fthree more serious patient safety
OL,11,Fissues and while this is happening
OL,12,Fthere is no investigation, there is no
OL,13,Freview taking place."
OL,15,FIn a statement, Swansea Bay University
OL,16,FHealth Board said:
OL,18,F"We can give firm assurances that the
OL,19,Fservice is not in a critical
OL,20,Fcondition."
